{"tid":1850783,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"喺catXman下單記得cap圖","createTime":"2020-01-29T17:00:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T01:01:55.000Z","uid":147209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b8adabe48d80711d46c51eaf54394b92cf1e27ab","tid":1850783,"uid":147209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:00:23.000Z","msg":"話說係12月尾靜雞雞訂左隻肥公仔，諗住送女友，見到1月20發貨，咁就落左單啦，比完錢email冇話預計送貨日期只話送貨通知你，都不以為然，過幾日上網睇賣晒，之後幾日又話有得預訂，但係已經話2月20號發貨囉， 心諗好彩落左單姐，點知等下等下到而家都未收到貨，咪係咁以send個message問下幾時有，等左幾日，終於有人覆，話你落單嗰陣時喺網頁上講咗話係二月尾先發貨，火都嚟啊，唔係等隻公仔開飯，但明明睇到係一月尾發貨，第一次買cap低，大佬點會估你遲呀，仲要話個客冇睇日期，真係嬲到想天花板，真係好唔愉快嘅經歷，無下次。"},{"pid":"5d7357bbb693e1b39005f0549108c1ca0dcd342c","tid":1850783,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/308/5d9705d903228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F308%2F5d9705d903228.jpg&h=786cb045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">種族清洗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n透過邊境不設防<br />\n高調宣揚非本地人士免費優先治療武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蓄意引導大量染病支那人來港<br />\n摧毀香港已經長期超負荷的醫療系統，令香港人大規模感染<br />\n而無法隔離或治理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n中共打算將香港將變成武漢，市民無法睇醫生，橫屍街頭<br />\n意圖對香港人進行大屠殺</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣東建國 香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dr